{"tid":528974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解渣馬啲工作人員會係一班童軍?","createTime":"2018-01-14T12:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T14:40:51.000Z","uid":136994,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9a7f623a6e1c4d9db0aefa786417a0b1e6351e","tid":528974,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"From 蘋果日報<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/194409_0fcfc06654a72d13e3029da114c30408.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F194409_0fcfc06654a72d13e3029da114c30408.png&h=c1d90f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實渣馬作為一間商業機構冠名贊助嘅活動，又有NIKE呢啲大型公司做sponsor (雖然係田總主辦)<br />\n呢一個活動嘅牟利同商業成分其實係overwhelming large，唔可以同賣旗同探訪老人院類比<br />\n搵一班咁細個嘅童軍去應付一個咁多人參與，係咪一件合理嘅事？一班個樣好明顯仲讀緊中學嘅童軍係咪真係有能力去處理呢啲logistic嘅嘢？舊年跑衫size問題搞到一班童軍無辜被屌，但童軍完全冇能力去handle<br />\n呢班童軍似乎都應該唔會有任何報酬，連車馬費都可能冇，童軍其實真係一種無償嘅勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a882ae42098f258a68266fd1d424cfb8af7c70c4","tid":528974,"uid":164770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"做登記同派野 應該冇所謂啦"},{"pid":"87ce66f605fd5052f252b22be1df02d5336e571e","tid":528974,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>From 蘋果日報<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/194409_0fcfc06654a72d13e3029da114c30408.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F194409_0fcfc06654a72d13e3029da114c30408.png&h=c1d90f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實渣馬作為一間商業機構冠名贊助嘅活動，又有NIKE呢啲大型公司做sponsor (雖然係田總主辦)<br />\n呢一個活動嘅牟利同商業成分其實係overwhelming large，唔可以同賣旗同探訪老人院類比<br />\n搵一班咁細個嘅童軍去應付一個咁多人參與<span style=\"color: red;\">嘅活動</span>，係咪一件合理嘅事？一班個樣好明顯仲讀緊中學嘅童軍係咪真係有能力去處理呢啲logistic嘅嘢？舊年跑衫size問題搞到一班童軍無辜被屌，但童軍完全冇能力去handle<br />\n呢班童軍似乎都應該唔會有任何報酬，連車馬費都可能冇，童軍其實真係一種無償嘅勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d34bb186dca2b2a2818ef3cfc90de8d717115f2b","tid":528974,"uid":60381,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"有車馬費 幾舊水<br />\n利申童軍 做過"},{"pid":"433ac05f33ef60729422a8edd61a0342a929339b","tid":528974,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:27:18.000Z","msg":"free"},{"pid":"0b797ac0abf132b9925a679ad057f0790813ae99","tid":528974,"uid":71655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4fa60859e3f35bd4b548f8c225b0265f32872ab","tid":528974,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"唔係點賺到盡"},{"pid":"b179736fb8bccc9bd45068496a561ab5edc3a402","tid":528974,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5196d83eac4eb562253467efe6f42870f0bcde11","tid":528974,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"做過一年，為做而做咁<br />\n當回憶都幾開心<br />\n繼續做就不了"},{"pid":"156fc636466bfffb60793d0de632ce7f37bcff37","tid":528974,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34bb186dca2b2a2818ef3cfc90de8d717115f2b","tid":528974,"uid":60381,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"有車馬費 幾舊水<br />\n利申童軍 做過"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"中學生都有？"},{"pid":"69084a478aa6a7063573f9115c4f62239ea92c52","tid":528974,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c5369916404d80ca8d9cf7d2